@PKUEcho See master/tensorflow/contrib/hvx for instructions on running HVX-accelerated TF on supported devices.
We don't currently have internal plans to add OpenCL support on Android, but if the community wants to add it that would be great. I have no idea what sort of issues might be run into though.
Otherwise I'd suggest the HVX option or waiting on CUDA support.

